metadata.name: Vision Strikers (LOGO) NO.1
metadata.description:
This series is the beginning of an exploration of the possibilities of esports and NFT, created by Duo, an esports team designer and NFT art creator. 
DRX VS will expand from Asia to the rest of the world.
